x4freetext: English translation
One surface-barrier semiconductor silicon
detector up to 400 mu-m thick with an angular
resolution of (+ -1) degr. was used for alpha-
particle detection.
A thin (1 mg/cm2) layer of melamine on a gold film
0.22 mg/cm2 thick was used as a target.

x4freetext: The absolute value of the differential cross

detected by the Faraday cup.
